“Laundry Quest: The App & Smart Washer System” – A system combining a mobile app with a smart washing machine that turns laundry into a role-playing game. Users create a character (a ‘Laundri Knight’ perhaps?), complete ‘missions’ (washing specific fabrics, sorting colors correctly), and earn rewards (virtual currency, access to new garment ‘skins’ for their character, discounts on laundry supplies). The smart washer tracks progress, provides guidance, and even incorporates mini-games (a color-matching puzzle while the machine is spinning). The app integrates with local dry cleaners, offering ‘side quests’ for stain removal and garment care. It even has a competitive leaderboard! Think ‘Pokemon Go’ meets ‘Stardew Valley’… but for clean clothes.